the male, with a more diVuse band of elongate setae on the anteromesial surface, than is seen in 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Kensley &amp; Schotte" authorityYear="2002" box="[253,404,1366,1390]" class="Malacostraca" family="Gnathostenetroididae" genus="Maresiella" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Isopoda" pageId="3" pageNumber="1423" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="aldabrana">
